---
const today = new Date();
const year = today.getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-slate-200 bg-white px-6 py-12 text-slate-600 dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-slate-400">
	<div class="mx-auto flex max-w-3xl flex-col gap-8 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
		<div class="max-w-md">
			<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
				Written, crafted, and quietly maintained by Giovanni.
			</p>
			<p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
				If something here was useful, say hello on
				<a
					href="https://twitter.com/giovannibenussi"
					target="_blank"
					class="underline decoration-slate-300 decoration-1 underline-offset-[3px] transition-colors hover:text-indigo-600 hover:decoration-indigo-500 dark:decoration-slate-600 dark:hover:text-indigo-300 dark:hover:decoration-indigo-400"
				>X<span class="inline-block ml-0.5 translate-y-[-1px] text-[0.85em] opacity-70" aria-hidden="true">↗</span></a>
				or poke around on
				<a
					href="https://github.com/giovannibenussi/"
					target="_blank"
					class="underline decoration-slate-300 decoration-1 underline-offset-[3px] transition-colors hover:text-indigo-600 hover:decoration-indigo-500 dark:decoration-slate-600 dark:hover:text-indigo-300 dark:hover:decoration-indigo-400"
				>GitHub<span class="inline-block ml-0.5 translate-y-[-1px] text-[0.85em] opacity-70" aria-hidden="true">↗</span></a>. You can also visit the
				<a
					href="/old"
					class="underline decoration-slate-300 decoration-1 underline-offset-[3px] transition-colors hover:text-indigo-600 hover:decoration-indigo-500 dark:decoration-slate-600 dark:hover:text-indigo-300 dark:hover:decoration-indigo-400"
				>old blog</a>.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-mono text-[11px] tracking-wider tabular-nums text-slate-400 sm:justify-end dark:text-slate-500">
			<span aria-hidden="true" class="inline-block size-1.5 translate-y-[-1px] bg-indigo-500 dark:bg-indigo-400"></span>
			<span>© {year} &middot; Giovanni Benussi</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>
